OL,7,FTom Barton was in Morpeth to watch the
OL,8,Fcyclists set off for their 1,000
OL,9,Fkilometre trip to Dorset
OL,11,FA brother and sister are taking on a
OL,12,F1,000 kilometre charity challenge in
OL,13,Fmemory of their father who died from
OL,14,Fmotor neurone disease.
OL,16,FDaniel and Amy Smith and three of
OL,17,Ftheir friends set off on Monday (29
OL,18,FApril) from Morpeth, heading to
OL,19,FNorfolk and Dorset - places chosen to
OL,20,Fspell out MND.
