OL,5,Cdad'
OL,7,FThey are riding in memory of their
OL,8,Ffather, accountant Mark Smith, who
OL,9,Fdied last year after being diagnosed
OL,10,Fwith the condition which affects the
OL,11,Fbrain and nerves.
OL,13,FMark's daughter Amy told ITV Tyne
OL,14,FTees: "He'd think we were bonkers,
OL,15,Fwhich we are, probably. But he'd be so
OL,16,Fproud, and I think he'd be absolutely
OL,17,Fblown away by the support that we've
OL,18,Fgot. He'd be so happy. So he's with us
OL,19,F- in spirit."
