OL,7,FHer bother Daniel said thinking of
OL,8,Ftheir father would be a "good
OL,9,Fmotivator" on their travels.
OL,11,F"If you're slightly in pain, it's
OL,12,Fnothing compared to what my dad and so
OL,13,Fmany others suffer," he added. "It
OL,14,Fdoes give you that boost - keeps you
OL,15,Fgoing."
OL,17,FIn his final months, Mark helped Amy
OL,18,Fand Daniel to put the trip together.
