OL,7,FAnd driving the support van, and
OL,8,Fwatching her kids take on the
OL,9,Fchallenge, is Mark's widow Helen.
OL,11,FShe said: "They're doing an amazing
OL,12,Fjob in memory of their dad. (I'm) so
OL,13,Fproud."
OL,15,FThe group has already raised more than
OL,16,F#20,000 for the MND Association.
OL,18,FDominic McDonough, from the charity
OL,19,Fsaid: "I think it's an absolutely epic
OL,20,Fchallenge. I mean, my legs hurt just
OL,21,Fthinking about it.
